Breach & Clear

Price InfoHistoryStatsRegions
WaitCollectIgnore
History Restricted
We are not allowed to show you historical data for Amazon
Shop Selection15 stores selected
Select:allmarkedinversenone
Marked stores are currently selling this game

Price OverviewPrice Detail

Price Overview chart shows development of price over time
  • How often is this game on sale? Are deals getting better?
  • How quickly did it reach current historical low?
  • Is historical low being repeated?
  • Is the regular price of the game dropping?
  • Do all stores drop price?
Price Detail chart shows a per-store view of price history
  • When and how good deals did a store have?
  • Do all stores have deals at the same time?
  • How much prices differ between stores?
  • Are there any differences between sale frequency?
\r\n

Cut OverviewSavings

Cut Overview chart shows development of price cuts over time
  • How often is this game on sale? What is the deals cut?
  • How often are deals repeated?
  • How quickly did price cuts reached current level?
Savings chart shows absolute value of price cut
If regular price drops, same price cut won't mean same savings
\r\n

Sales DistributionSales Duration

Sales distribution chart can tell you when there usually is a sale during a year
  • When are deals more frequent?
  • Are deals with higher cut more frequent during certain time of year?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores
Sales duration chart may tell you how long a sale usually lasts
  • Do deals with smaller cut last longer? By how much?
  • What is a median duration of a sale?
  • How many times was a game on sale with a price cut?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores

Breach & Clear brings deep tactical strategy to mobile devices! Build your Special Operations team, plan and execute advanced missions, and own every angle.\r\rChoose your real-world squad -- US Army Rangers, US Navy Seals, Canadas JTF2, and more -- and take on a variety of foes with different skill-sets and abilities. Learn to approach, engage, and dominate your opponent through superior tactics and training, while leveling your characters in one of the deepest progression systems created for mobile devices.\r\r** FULL CUSTOMIZATION **\rBuild your arsenal with thousands of gun combinations, and specialize each soldier with a combination of perks, tactics, camo, armor, and inventory all tailored by you. Tune your load-out with consumables like UAV Drones and Breaching Charges that can change the course of battle!\r\r** OWN EVERY ANGLE **\rEach soldier matters, every decision counts. Plan your mission step-by-step: split up your team and assault the map from multiple entrance points, set routes and fields of fire, use cover and outflank your foe.\r\r** REALISTIC, TACTICAL COMBAT **\rDeveloped with help from members of the Special Operations Forces community, Breach & Clear features actual close-quarters combat tactics and a variety of door-breaching techniques. Soldiers equip real-world weapons and gear. Firefights take place in real time.\r\rThe world of Breach & Clear is constantly evolving, with new maps, gear, game modes, and squads coming soon.
— Metacritic.com
